all-round partnership of good-neighborliness and mutual trust
which can be seen as an example of good-neighborly friendship and
mutually beneficial cooperation between countries with different
social systems," he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said that to further consolidate and develop the friendly
relations and cooperation between China and Thailand not only
conforms to the fundamental interests of the two countries and the
common aspiration of the two peoples, but also conduces to peace,
stability and development in the region.
</P>
