Hendrawan will meet Haryanto Arbi in the semi-finals. Singapore
Open champion Arbi beat Rudy Ignatius, also from Indonesia, with
15-5, 15-7.
</P>
<P>
The 18-year-old Taufik Hidayat beat Tomas Johansson from Sweden
with 15-6,15-10, and will meet Yan Yong Jyen in the semi-finals.
</P>
<P>
In the men's doubles, Indonesia had four pairs in the semi-
finals. They are top seed Candra Wijaya/Tony Gunawan, Olympic
champion Ricky A. Subagja/Rexy Mainaky, Antonius Budiaryanto/Halim
Haryanto and Flandy Limpele/Wahyu Agung. 
</P>
