scholars gathered here today to celebrate the tenth anniversary of
the Russian Branch of the Western Returned Students' Association (
WRSA).
</P>
<P>
Zhu Xun, chairman of the Russian Branch of WRSA, addressed the
meeting, praising members of the branch for making enormous
contributions to the construction of the homeland and in promoting
the traditional friendship between China and Russia.
