develop the relationship across the Taiwan Strait and to advance
the country's reunification cause," said Hu. Anyone attempting to
obstruct this historical trend will do so in vain.
</P>
<P>
Storace reiterated that Uruguay will unswervingly keep to the "
One-China" policy, and it will, as always, support China's
peaceful reunification cause. "Uruguay will continue to enhance
its friendship and cooperative relations with China," he said.
</P>
