two states" statement undermined the basis of cross-straits
dialogue and negotiation, and fundamentally contradicts and
compromises the interests of Taiwan compatriots.
</P>
<P>
All attendants warned that Lee should stop playing with fire,
halt at the brink of the precipice, and abandon the so-called "two
states" statements, otherwise he will become the sinner of the
Chinese nation. 
