<HEADLINE> CPC Senior Official Meets CIS Trade Union Delegates </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Wei Jianxing, a standing
committee member of the Political Bureau of the Chinese Communist
Party (CPC) Central Committee, met with Vladimir Scherbakov,
president of the General Confederation of Trade Unions (GCTU) of
the Commonwealth of Independent States (CIS) and delegates from
trade unions of CIS member countries here today.
</P>
<P>
Wei, who is also member of the Secretariat of the CPC Central
Committee and chairman of the All-China Federation of Trade Unions
(ACFTU), briefed the guests on China's current political and
economic situation as well as the work of the trade unions.
</P>
