GCTU and trade unions of CIS member countries, he said.
</P>
<P>
Scherbakov spoke highly of China's great achievements over the
past 50 years, especially since it introduced reform and opening
up, and praised the important role of Chinese trade unions in the
country's reform and development.
</P>
<P>
He gave a briefing about the present political and economic
situation of CIS countries and the work of the GCTU.
</P>
<P>
Scherbakov and his party are here for a week-long international
symposium on the work of trade unions in the period of transition
to the market economy, which opened today. The symposium is co-
sponsored by the ACFTU and the GCTU.  
