active part in cooperating in the Lancang-Mekong River basin
development. We attach great importance to the ASEAN Vision 2020
and the Hanoi Plan of Action, and hope to deepen cooperation with
ASEAN in the economic, trade, scientific and technological, social
and other fields," he said.
</P>
<P>
China and ASEAN have become each other's important trade and
investment partners, he said, adding that China has signed or
issued documents for the 21st-century-oriented cooperation with
Thailand, Vietnam Malaysia and Brunei, and it hopes to further
deepen the mutually beneficial cooperation with all ASEAN
countries.
</P>
