At the threshold of the new century, he said, the Asian people
are thinking about the future of Asia and that of the world as
well.
</P>
<P>
How to continue the efforts to promote the establishment of a
just and reasonable new international political and economic order
of peace and stability and work hard to bring into the 21st
century of a new Asia and a new world with lasting pace and
universal prosperity? Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
These are the pressing tasks to be tackled by the statemen and
people from Asia, including China and Thailand, and the rest of
the world, Jiang said. 
